snippet.title: Best VGM 1993 - Doom - The Demons From Adrian's Pen (E2M2 ~ Containment Area)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 666 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ft-qnOD77V4

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC, 3DO, SNES etc.
Doom (1993)
The Demons From Adrian's Pen (E2M2 ~ Containment Area)
Robert Prince
